OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fcontinues across the north this
OL,7,Fevening and overnight as cloud
OL,8,Fthickens and lowers across the region.
OL,9,FA warm night to come but turning
OL,10,Fbreezier by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudier day on Saturday
OL,13,Fas rain becomes confined to higher
OL,14,Fground. Brighter spells possible in
OL,15,Fthe south by late afternoon, where
OL,16,Fit'll feel warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
